            <marc:subfield code="v">v.1</marc:subfield>
            <marc:subfield code="x">"Most respectable sir, At a time, like this, when literary productions are so cheap, and literary merit is so much disregarded, you will permit me to lay at your feet this little piece; in favour of which, I promise myself to meet with your patronage and protection."</marc:subfield>
